---
import Button from '../../Button.astro';
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-36 bg-warm-cream">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-storehouse-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase reveal">
        The invitation
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-6 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-text-deep leading-[1.05] reveal reveal-delay-1">
        Start with peace.<br />
        Go as deep as you want.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-10 max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-lg text-text-body leading-relaxed reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p>
          You don't have to believe everything on this page to use Storehouse.
        </p>
        <p>
          On the surface, Storehouse gives you one number &mdash; what's safe to spend. That alone can bring clarity and peace.
        </p>
        <p>
          But if you want to go deeper, there's a philosophy here. A way of thinking about margin, generosity, and trust that can transform your relationship with money.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pull quote -->
      <div class="mt-12 reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <p class="font-quote text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-text-deep italic leading-snug">
          "Take what's helpful. Leave what's not."
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12 reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <Button href="/waitlist" variant="primary" size="lg">
          Join the Waitlist
        </Button>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-muted">
          Launching soon. Free to start. No credit card.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
